archimate:ApplicationComponent.name: Business.gov.nl
archimate:ApplicationComponent.documentation:
Business.gov.nl is the Point of Single Contact (PSC) for resident and foreign entrepreneurs who want to establish a business or do business in the Netherlands
Business.gov.nl is the English-language counterpart of Ondernemersplein. The website was launched in August 2017 and is an initiative of the Ministry of the Interior and Kingdom Relations.
